data.description: This adorable 4 bedroom 3 1/2 bath home is move-in ready. The primary bedroom has its' own fireplace, a walk-in closet, and you can add a seating area. This property has a spiral staircase, intercom system, high ceilings, new central air and heat unit, and a new garage door. There is a beautiful fountain that provides a calming effect.  Add your special touch to this property and make this your new home! This house won't last for long!
